Hi, I don't know if I'm doing things wrong.

The indicator for depleted fuel no longer appears in the parts info, it only shows enriched uranium.

For example, at the SPH, if I decide to use the MF-2 Nuclear Drum, it only shows me enriched uranium.

 

 

Could you help me with this?
